cd ~
cd /mnt/c/temp

sudo apt-get update
curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_14.x | sudo -E bash -
sudo apt-get install -y nodejs

sudo pm2 start app.js

sudo /etc/init.d/nginx start

Install Express
npm install express

Installing other 3rd party libraries
npm install bootstrap@next jquery popper

Install the DynamoDB dependancy
npm install @aws-sdk/client-dynamodb

Installing S3 dependancy
npm install @aws-sdk/client-s3

Installing EC2 dependancy 
npm install @aws-sdk/client-ec2

Installing Monolithic AWS package
npm install aws-sdk

Accessing the DynamoDB using the API
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/Using.API.html

Getting started with the NodeJS and the DynamoDB 
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/amazondynamodb/latest/developerguide/SettingUp.html


Accessing the DynamoDB - 
Create a Administrator IAM role

